OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780589464
OL,3,CFire crews working to extinguish large
OL,4,Cfire at TATA Steel
OL,6,FFire crews have been working
OL,7,Fthroughout the night to tackle a fire
OL,8,Fat the Tata steelworks in Port Talbot
OL,10,FResidents from mile away said they
OL,11,Fcould hear alarms sounding and could
OL,12,Fsmell the smoke.
OL,14,FIn a statement released at 8am this
OL,15,Fmorning Tata said: "Mid and West Wales
OL,16,FFire Service attended the Port Talbot
OL,17,Fsite last night at around 8pm to deal
OL,18,Fwith a fire at one of the site's
OL,19,Fprocessing lines. All personnel were
OL,20,Faccounted for and evacuated from the
OL,21,Farea safely.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
