OL,3,CFire crews working to extinguish large
OL,4,Cfire at TATA Steel
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police advised residents
OL,7,Fto keep windows and doors closed and
OL,8,Fasked people to avoid the area.
OL,10,FRapid Relief Team UK who provide
OL,11,Fsupport to emergency services were in
OL,12,Fattendance at the described the
OL,13,Fincident a "significant fire".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
