OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780589464
OL,3,CFire crews working to extinguish large
OL,4,Cfire at TATA Steel
OL,6,FThey said: "Emergency crews have been
OL,7,Fworking through the night at a major
OL,8,Fincident at Tata Steelworks in Port
OL,9,FTalbot, involving a significant fire.
OL,10,FWith 8 fire appliances, 2 foam units,
OL,11,F2 high-reach turntable platforms and
OL,12,Fan HVP on scene, around 100 responders
OL,13,Ffaced an incredibly demanding and
OL,14,Fhazardous night's work.
OL,16,F"RRT volunteers arrived on site within
OL,17,F90 minutes of callout, serving 125 hot
OL,18,Fmeals through the night to keep crews
OL,19,Ffuelled as they continued their vital
OL,20,Fwork.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
